palettes/mard.json

The color data in palettes/mard.json (MARD classic solid set, series A-H and M)
is derived from the "beadcolors" project by maxcleme, which is distributed under
the MIT License. The RGB values were converted from the upstream CSV
raw/mard.csv into the "#RRGGBB" hex form used by this project and filtered to the
221 solid-series colors; no color values were otherwise modified.

